metadata.description: AI Birthday Moons is a line of curated, AI-generated Happy Birthday cards offered through NFTgreetings.xyz. Our minting app applows you to mint one (or more) directly to your friend's ETH wallet where it'll continue to wish your friend Happy Birthday for many years to come. (Well, unless the collection "moons" and your friend sells it!) We've popped some of the prompt wording into the metadata, but keep in mind that AI can (and does) do some weird stuff with the input. Thanks for collecting! From all of us at GenerativeNFTs.io. :-)
metadata.name: AI Birthday Moons #1
